<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_323" id="161r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_323_r1l30">vlm <expan>Nördlling<ex>en</ex></expan> / dinkelſpühel . <expan>h<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>H<ex>einrich</ex></expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Türe<ex>n</ex>vvank</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_323_r1l31">/ Hall . <expan>Heylprun<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_323_r1l32">Als wir ew nehſt <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd <expan>gepet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vns die <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>cʒeleıh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_323_r1l33">vnd 
<del rend="strikethrough">gen Onelſpach </del> cʒü den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>cʒeſchicke<ex>n</ex></expan> gen Onelſpach auf ſant Egıdıen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_323_r1l34">tag / <expan>Laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> erſam <expan>fruntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> <expan>vvıſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> / daʒ vns derſelb tag auch <expan>vvıd<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_323_r1l35">boten vnd aber ab iſt / diſelb botſchaft vns auf hewte cʒe <expan>mittetag</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_323_r1l36">erſt kumen ıſt / . <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in die <expan>ſ<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>ı</expan> <expan>Bartholo<ex>m</ex>eȷ</expan> . </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_323" id="161r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Ulm, <expan>Nördlling<ex>en</ex></expan>, Dinkelspühel,
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>H<ex>einrich</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Türe<ex>n</ex>wank</expan>, Hall,
                        <expan>Heylprun<ex>n</ex></expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Als wir ew nehst <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und <expan>gepet<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, uns die <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>cze leih<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und czü den
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>cze schicke<ex>n</ex></expan> gen Onelspach auf <app><note><q type="date">sant Egidien tag</q>01.09.1411</note></app>,
                                <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> ersam
                                <expan>fruntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>
<expan>wisse<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz uns derselb tag auch
                                <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> boten und aber ab ist, diselb
                        botschaft uns auf hewte cze <expan>mittetag</expan> erst kumen ist.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in die
                            <expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>i</expan>
<expan>Bartholo<ex>m</ex>ei</expan>.</ab>
</div>
